      <description>Kurdish ambitions in Syria are consistent with the establishment of a democratic, civil and pluralistic state that guarantees full rights for all ethnic and religious minorities, according to the authors. Blocking them from participating in Geneva will only “escalate the tragic situation on the ground”.</description>
